     <item>
       <title>Javascript Throttling</title>
       <link>/posts/javascript-throttling/</link>
       <pubDate>Sat, 25 Jul 2020 10:19:18 +0200</pubDate>
       
       <guid>/posts/javascript-throttling/</guid>
       <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello everyone!
This post will be about a parallel computing trick I had to use.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So I needed to limit the number of requests which are fired towards a third party API at the same time because of low threshold for DDoS there.
Requests were sent from several places but both written in typescript so that is what I am going to use here.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TL;DR;&lt;br&gt;
Here is the final function if you just want to copy and paste this for typescript:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-typescript&#34; data-lang=&#34;typescript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;async&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;throttleAllAsync&lt;/span&gt;(
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;,
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; (() &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;any&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;)[]) {
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;slice&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;).&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;map&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt;());
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;length&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;++&lt;/span&gt;) {
        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromise&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;any&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;]().&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;(() &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;splice&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;indexOf&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromise&lt;/span&gt;)));
        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;push&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromise&lt;/span&gt;);
        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;length&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt;) {
            &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;race&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;);
        }
    }

    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;all&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;);
}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Or this for javascript:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-javascript&#34; data-lang=&#34;javascript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;async&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;throttleAllAsync&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;) {
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;slice&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;).&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;map&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt; =&amp;gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt;());
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;length&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;++&lt;/span&gt;) {
        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromise&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;]().&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;(() =&amp;gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;splice&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;indexOf&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromise&lt;/span&gt;)));
        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;push&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromise&lt;/span&gt;);
        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;length&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt;) {
            &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; Promise.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;race&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;);
        }
    }

    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; Promise.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;all&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;);
}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;You are still here? Good!
Let&amp;rsquo;s retrace the steps I did while creating this function.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Keep in mind, I have only been doing js/ts for a couple of months, so a lot of thing I just had to figure out from scratch.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;First I needed a way to run all promises. That&amp;rsquo;s easy!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-typescript&#34; data-lang=&#34;typescript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;all&lt;/span&gt;([]);
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;And then the target function signature is&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-typescript&#34; data-lang=&#34;typescript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;async&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;throttleAllAsync&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promises&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;any&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;[])
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unfortunately there is no way to configure the maximum number of promises being currently executed for &lt;code&gt;Promise.all&lt;/code&gt;.
Also as soon as you create a promise it already starts execution.
The only thing that await or &lt;code&gt;Promise.all&lt;/code&gt; do is that they wait for the result to be available.
They have nothing to do with the actual execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With this in mind let&amp;rsquo;s change the signature to something which will not run the promises before we need it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-typescript&#34; data-lang=&#34;typescript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;async&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;throttleAllAsync&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; (() &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;any&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;)[])
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Here. Now the caller has to pass lambda&amp;rsquo;s or functions which create promises.
Now. Let&amp;rsquo;s use &lt;code&gt;Promise.all&lt;/code&gt; but only for a slice of the array.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-typescript&#34; data-lang=&#34;typescript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;async&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;throttleAllAsync&lt;/span&gt;(
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;,
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; (() &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;any&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;)[]) {
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;slice&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt;).&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;map&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt;());
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;all&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;);
}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;This will run first &lt;code&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/code&gt; of promises. Let&amp;rsquo;s make it so it runs all of them eventually.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-typescript&#34; data-lang=&#34;typescript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;async&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;throttleAllAsync&lt;/span&gt;(
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;,
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; (() &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;any&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;)[]) {
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;;
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;length&lt;/span&gt;) {
        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;slice&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;, Math.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;min&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;length&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt;)).&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;map&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt;());
        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;all&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;);
    }
}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;This is good but there is one issue.
It doesn&amp;rsquo;t always run &lt;code&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/code&gt; of promises. As soon as one finishes, then one less are running at the same time.
We would want to be a bit more effective.
But how do we add a promise as soon as one of them finishes?
Well, for that we are going to use&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-typescript&#34; data-lang=&#34;typescript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;race&lt;/span&gt;([]);
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;This function await till any one of the promises finishes.
So we can wait for any one to finish and then add a new one to the array.
We also need to remove the finished one. We can do this by using &lt;code&gt;then&lt;/code&gt; on a promise to then also remove it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-typescript&#34; data-lang=&#34;typescript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;async&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;throttleAllAsync&lt;/span&gt;(
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;,
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; (() &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;any&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;)[]) {
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;slice&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;).&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;map&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt;());
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;length&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;++&lt;/span&gt;) {
        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromise&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;any&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;]().&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;(() &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;splice&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;indexOf&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromise&lt;/span&gt;)));
        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;push&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromise&lt;/span&gt;);
        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;race&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;);
    }

    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;length&lt;/span&gt;) {
        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;race&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;);
    }
}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are almost there!
There are still two thing to improve here.
Firtly, we don&amp;rsquo;t need to race them one by one at the end, we can just use te Promise.all that we saw earlier.
Secondly, though Promise.race waits for any one promise to finish, several can in fact finish before we add more to the pool.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Including these two ideas brings us to the final code!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-typescript&#34; data-lang=&#34;typescript&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;async&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;throttleAllAsync&lt;/span&gt;(
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;number&lt;/span&gt;,
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; (() &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;any&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;)[]) {
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;slice&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;).&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;map&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;p&lt;/span&gt;());
    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;length&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;++&lt;/span&gt;) {
        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromise&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;any&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;promiseProducers&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;]().&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;(() &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;splice&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;indexOf&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromise&lt;/span&gt;)));
        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;push&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromise&lt;/span&gt;);
        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;length&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/span&gt;) {
            &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;race&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;);
        }
    }

    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;all&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;activePromises&lt;/span&gt;);
}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Here!&lt;br&gt;
Now we can run requests in parallel but no more then &lt;code&gt;maximumLevelOfParallelism&lt;/code&gt; at a time.
Thank you for reading and see you next time!&lt;/p&gt;
